The assert helper uses grep -qF. Strings starting with --- are
interpreted as grep options, causing 'unrecognized option' errors.
Use a substring without the leading dashes, or switch to grep -qe.

Hit this in the follow test: assert 'edges section' '--- edges ---'
failed because grep saw --- as a flag.
